 "textcontent_fbxcsdr13ui_html": "At Animal Pride\u2122 we love animals! We are a collection of pet parents who put an equal amount of passion and dedication into our business as we do with our pets, aiming to offer the largest selection of high quality pet &amp; animal inspired apparel for people.<div><br><div>&nbsp;A percentage of the sales from AnimalPride.com are donated to support various animal causes.&nbsp;<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>&nbsp;We also support artists. We source many of our amazing graphics from artists and believe that by focusing on quality apparel and partnering with great artists we will be able to create inspiring products that people love and remember.<\/div><\/div>",
